'''禁止化學武器組織'''（{{lang-en|'''Organization for the Prohibition of Chemical Weapons'''}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]：{{lang|en|'''OPCW'''}}），是一個於1997年成立的[[國際組織|國際組織]]<ref name="formation" />，總部設於[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[海牙|海牙]]，與[[聯合國|聯合國]]密切合作，是為執行《[[禁止化学武器公约|禁止化学武器公约]]》而創立的，以實地查察等方式，推行禁用及銷毀化學武器的工作。<ref name="NYT-20131011" />

2013年10月11日，[[挪威诺贝尔委员会|挪威诺贝尔委员会]]公布，「因其對消除化學武器的多方努力」，頒授2013年[[諾貝爾和平獎|諾貝爾和平獎]]給禁止化學武器組織<ref name="Peace2013" />。

== 成員國 ==
所有《[[禁止化學武器公約|禁止化學武器公約]]》締約國均自動成為禁止化學武器組織成員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.opcw.org/about-opcw/member-states/ |title=OPCW Member States |publisher=Opcw.org |date= |accessdate=2013-10-11 |archive-date=2018-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929130805/https://www.opcw.org/about-opcw/member-states/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。只有[[以色列|以色列]]並非成員國，全因其簽署並未獲得承認。而[[北朝鮮|北朝鮮]]和[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]則沒有簽署公約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.opcw.org/about-opcw/non-member-states/ |title=Non-Member States |publisher=Opcw.org |date= |accessdate=2013-10-11 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012051136/http://www.opcw.org/about-opcw/non-member-states/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。埃及方面表示，若以色列签署《[[不扩散核武器条约|不扩散核武器条约]]》，埃及将会签署禁止化學武器公約<ref name="Egypt-Israel">{{Cite news |first=Barak |last=Ravid |url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/.premium-1.546613 |title=Israel adamant it won't ratify chemical arms treaty before hostile neighbors |work=[[国土报|国土报]] |date=2013-09-12 |accessdate=2018-01-03 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924172400/http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/.premium-1.546613 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Egypt-refusing-to-sign-WMD-treaties |title=Egypt refusing to sign WMD treaties |work=[[耶路撒冷邮报|耶路撒冷邮报]] |date=2009-05-13 |accessdate=2013-11-01 |archive-date=2021-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216141653/https://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Egypt-refusing-to-sign-WMD-treaties |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |first=Joel |last=Gulhane |url=http://www.dailynewsegypt.com/2013/11/10/arab-league-discusses-wmds-at-egypts-request/ |title=Arab League discusses WMDs at Egypt's request |work=Daily News Egypt |date=2013-11-10 |accessdate=2018-01-03 |archive-date=2021-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216135211/https://dailynewsegypt.com/2013/11/10/arab-league-discusses-wmds-at-egypts-request/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。以色列方面