總幹事的任期為4年，但第一任總幹事何塞·毛里西奧·布斯塔尼在其第二任期中只任職了一年左右。這是因為成員國對布斯塔尼缺乏信心，所以致使他被解僱。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.opcw.org/index.php?eID=dam_frontend_push&docID=5103 |title = Draft decision of the First Special Session of the Conference of the States Parties of the OPCW |date =  |accessdate = 2013-10-11 |archive-date = 2012-10-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022182047/http://www.opcw.org/index.php?eID=dam_frontend_push&docID=5103 |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/1944879.stm | work=BBC News | title=Chemical weapons body sacks head | date=22 April 2002 | accessdate=19 August 2010 | archive-date=2007-03-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070313145747/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/1944879.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>成員國美國指出布斯塔尼共有三個原因讓成員國對其失去信心，分別是：「兩極化和對抗性的行為」、「管理不善」和「在禁止化學武器組織中倡導不合時宜的職位」。<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://2001-2009.state.gov/t/ac/rls/fs/9120.htm|title=Preserving the Chemical Weapons Convention: The Need For A New Organization for the Prohibition of Chemical Weapons (OPCW) Director-General|date=2002-04-01|accessdate=2013-10-11|publisher=US [[Bureau_of_Arms_Control|Bureau of Arms Control]]|archive-date=2013-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013034456/http://2001-2009.state.gov/t/ac/rls/fs/9120.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

可是，解僱隨後被[[國際勞工組織|國際勞工組織]]行政法庭確定為不當的，並要求禁止化學武器組織賠償布斯塔尼50,000歐元作為精神損害賠償、給予他第二任期的所有工資、並代他交付法律費用。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ilo.org/dyn/triblex/triblexmain.fullText?p_lang=en&p_judgment_no=2232&p_language_code=EN |title=the ILO decision |accessdate=2013-10-13 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012053610/http://www.ilo.org/dyn/triblex/triblexmain.fullText?p_lang=en&p_judgment_no=2232&p_language_code=EN |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 與聯合国的關係 ==
此組織並非[[聯合國|聯合國]]的下屬機構，但與聯合國在政策和實際問題上合作。於2000年9月7日，禁止化學武器組織和聯合國簽署了合作協議。該協議列出了他們將會合作的項目。<ref name="UN_ARES55283">{{UN document |docid=A-RES-55-283 |type=Resolution |body=General Assembly |session=55 |accessdate=21 August 2007}}</ref>自此，禁止化學武器組織的調查員便可用[[聯合國通行證|聯合國通行證]]到達目標國。<ref>[http://books.google.nl/books?id=Y36eYpRtWXIC&lpg=PA336&ots=fG643cWxqZ&dq=exchange%20of%20letters%20OPCW%20UN&hl=en&pg=PA336#v=onepage&q&f=false OPCW, The Legal Texts] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.nl/books?id=Y36eYpRtWXIC&lpg=PA336&ots=fG643cWxqZ&dq=exchange%20of%20letters%20OPCW%20UN&hl=en&pg=PA336#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20131014063935 }} TMC Asser Press, p336</ref>同時，[[联合国区域集团|联合国区域集团]]亦會監管禁止化學武器組織的執行理事會，並提供非正式的討論平台。<ref name=NTI1/>

== 2013年諾貝爾和平獎 ==
2013年，禁止化學武器組織獲頒[[諾貝爾和平獎|諾貝爾和平獎]]<ref>[http://www.apdnews.com/news/37088.html 禁化武组织获2013年诺贝尔和平奖] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013214129/http://www.apdnews.com/news/37088.html |date=2013-10-13 }}，亚太日报，2013年10月12日</ref>，表彰其「對消除[[化學武器|化學武器]]的多方努力」<ref name="Peace2013">{{cite web |url= http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/2013/press.pdf |title= 2013年諾貝爾和平獎 |publisher= [[諾貝爾基金會|諾貝爾基金會]] |accessdate= 2013-10-10 |archive-date= 2013-10-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131014090534/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/2013/press.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref>。在官方公佈得主的1[[小時|小時]]前，[[挪威廣播公司|挪威廣播公司]]就已經洩漏禁止化學武器組織獲獎的消息了<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/330470/news/world/chemical-weapons-watchdog-opcw-to-win-nobel-peace-prize-nrk-says |title=Chemical weapons watchdog OPCW to win Nobel Peace Prize, NRK says {{!}} News {{!}} GMA News Online |access-date=2013-10-11 |archive-date=2013-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014090509/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/330470/news/world/chemical-weapons-watchdog-opcw-to-win-nobel-peace-prize-nrk-says |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

授獎獻詞的用語極具針對性，包括「[[2013年叙利亚化学武器袭击事件|最近在敘利亞发生的事件中]]，化學武器再度被滥用」「尤其是[[美國|美國]]與[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]，沒有遵守於2012年4月的最後期限前銷毀[[大规模杀伤性武器|WMD]]的規定」<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24490925 |title = Syria chemical weapons monitors win Nobel Peace Prize |date = 2013-10-11 |accessdate = 2013-10-12 |publisher = [[BBC_News|BBC News]] |archive-date = 2021-02-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210216135237/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24490925 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=nobelpr/>。此次授獎，顯然是對[[國際|國際]][[危機|危機]]的及時回應。<ref name="NYT-20131011">{{cite news |last=Cowell |first=Alan |title=Chemical Weapons Watchdog Wins Nobel Peace Prize |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/12/world/chemical-weapons-watchdog-wins-nobel-peace-prize.html |date=11 October 2013 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=11 October 2013 |archive-date=2021-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216135255/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/12/world/chemical-weapons-watchdog-wins-nobel-peace-prize.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/Chemicals-weapons-watchdog-OPCW-wins-Nobel-peace-prize/articleshow/23970428.cms?utm_source=facebook.com&utm_medium=referral | title=Chemicals weapons watchdog OPCW wins Nobel peace prize | publisher=Times of India | date=11 October 2013 | accessdate=11 October 2013 | archive-date=2020-02-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200219014527/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/Chemicals-weapons-watchdog-OPCW-wins-Nobel-peace-prize/articleshow/23970428.cms?utm_source=facebook.com&utm_medium=referral | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/10/11/wins-2013-nobel-peace-prize/ |title = Global chemical weapons watchdog wins 2013 Nobel Peace Prize |publisher = Fox News |date = 11 October 2013 |accessdate = 11 October 2013 |archive-date = 2013-10-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131011092129/http://www